<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink391" corresp="#TNV23poem11">
<l>maṟuvi ṟūvic ciṟukaruṅ kākkai</l>
<l>yaṉpuṭai marapiṉiṉ kiḷaiyō ṭārap</l>
<l>paccūṉ peyta painniṇa valci</l>
<l>polampuṉai kalattiṟ ṟarukuveṉ mātō</l>
<l>veñciṉa viṟalvēṟ kāḷaiyo</l>
<l>ṭañci lōtiyai varakkarain tīmē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O small black crow with flawless feathers! </l>
<l>I will serve you with food, [comprising of] fresh meet with fat poured on it, </l>
<l>in a pot decorated with gold, so that [you] eat your fill with your kin </l>
<l>[that has] the tradition of kindness. </l>
<l>Please call the girl with pretty hair to come </l>
<l>together with the man of victorious spear and hot anger! </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
